reviews:
I’d give it zero if I could. DISGUSTING venue that made me drink ANTS.

I went there on a night out with a few friends. Ordered a drink and noticed something on my ice, I assumed it was fruit remains. I carried on drinking and noticed a few things in my drink, pulled out my straw to poke it and there were DEAD ANTS all stuck to my straw, and multiple dead ants in my drink.

I’ve gone to the bar to complain about this and say I wanted a whole refund for all of our drinks that we’d just ordered (our drinks were untouched at this point) and said I wanted to leave the bar in general as I felt sick and was disgusted. They refused to refund the drinks, and I had to sit uncomfortably in a venue that had just made me drink ANTS because we’d spent all our money in there. They didn’t even try to see what the problem was or how these ants had ended up dead in my drink.

I then emailed head office, MONTHS later and no one has got back to me.

To top it off I commented on their socials, guess what, ALL MY COMMENTS WERE DELETED.

This establishment and company couldn’t get any worse. I’ve spoken to people and as soon as they heard which be at one they were they all had their own story on how disgusting that place is. Hope it gets shut down and I will continue posting these reviews until someone gets back to me.

As I said on social media you can delete my comments on Instagram but you CANNOT delete Google reviews, so Goodluck.
C D, thank you for leaving us feedback. We are disappointed to hear that your experience was not a positive one. Please contact us at 020 7978 6595 so we can work with you to make this right.

Tonight, my fiancé and I decided to go out for a couple of drinks. We have always known of Be at One as it’s a chain, but have never been. I must say that this customer service is EXCEPTIONAL. I will never forget the experience that Paul and Tobia have provided. Thank you so much for making us feel good and welcomed.
Kamila Grasmane, we are so pleased you enjoyed your visit to Be At One - Battersea Rise!
Pol is always helpful, friendly and nice with us! He’s the best bartender ever! I’m a loyal customer as I receive the best service .
Fanny Karina Carrillo, thank you for your kind words and this wonderful review!

Dominic was an amazing bartender. The drinks were strong and worth the money. Our best tip is to go during happy hour. On Sundays it’s quite quiet so if you wish to visit when it’s less busy, Sunday is your day to go.
Ky Montana, we are so pleased you enjoyed your visit to Be At One - Battersea Rise! We look forward to your next visit! Take care!
Better experience I had in Clapham, great music and great people, Carltone and Dominic looked after us and were really nice to all of us. I recommend 1000% when those guys are there!!!
Lucas Cookie, we're so glad that we were able to go above and beyond your expectations! Thanks again for the recommendation, and have an amazing day!

Lovely place and lovely staff!!! The midget Colombian guy was espetacular!!! I will definitely recommend this place to my friends and I’ll come back for sure. Even tho I only had fruit juice all night, I loved the atmosphere! Best bar in London.
Lucas Prazeres, reviews like this give us motivation and help us ensure we provide high-quality care. Thank you, and have a fantastic day!

Every time I come to this bar I just always have the best time. Not only the play the best music and serve the best cocktails, but they also serve you and treat you with so much kindness. Love this place and everyone that works here, especially Michael who has been here for a while already and stil doing a great job!
Hello Vale Bella R T, thank you; we appreciate your feedback! We look forward to your next visit! Take care!

Been here a few times now - can not fault the service and customer experience. Dom and Carlton have been the bartenders tonight and the service has been excellent. Would highly recommend this bar to anyone in the area, amazing cocktails and vibes.

Hi George Way, thank you for taking the time to leave a review for us at Be At One - Battersea Rise. We're happy we could meet your expectations! Thanks again for the recommendation, and have an amazing day!

Had an amazing time at Be at one last night. All of the staff were amazing! Was greeted by very kind and welcoming security on the door called Ryan and Chelsea who were very friendly. The bar staff were so quick and efficient despite being busy all night but still managed to serve beautiful tasting cocktails with a smile. Big shout to Dom, Tobia, Pol, Carltone and Micky who entertained us while serving. They were all very attentive and made it a lovely experience all round. Top staff!
Thank you again for taking the time to let us know how we did. We hope you have a great day!

Be At One in Battersea is the best. Dominic and Ronnie are masterful cocktail makers. I always come here when I want a good night out. (P.s I am writing this under duress in order to get 2 cocktails for £12...but jokes aside its actually great)
Hello Jonathan Ross, thank you; we appreciate your feedback! We look forward to your next visit! Take care!
